<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="16Jul1929"><font color="red">16 July 1929</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to Harriet Weaver): Everyone seems delighted with this place &hellip; James Stephens is coming down here on Saturday (20 July 1929) for a weekend to talk about my book &hellip; He seemed &hellip; moved by my proposal to hand over the work to him if I found my sight or the opposition demanded it &hellip; I thought it better my proposal to James Stephens should come now so that if I am forced to it in the end it may appear less abrupt </div>
